1. *Dopustili* su mi da odemo na putovanje. (They allowed me to go on a trip.)
2. Njegovi roditelji nisu mu *dopustili* da izađe van. (His parents didn't let him go out.)
3. Imamo dozvolu da *dopustimo* deci da izađu van. (We have permission to let the children go out.)
4. Oni nisu hteli da *dopuste* da se slika objavi. (They didn't want to allow the picture to be published.)
5. Moraš da se *dopustiš* da se promeniš. (You have to allow yourself to change.)